title: Switzerland Youth Unemployment Rate
description: Youth Unemployment Rate in Switzerland decreased to 2.10 percent in September from 2.20 percent in August of 2022. Youth Unemployment Rate in Switzerland averaged 3.53 percent from 1993 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 6.10 percent in December of 1993 and a record low of 1.40 percent in June of 2001. This page provides - Switzerland Youth Unemployment Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: State Secretariat for Economic Affairs
